00:36:39,614 --> 00:36:42,279
( Aplausos )

738
00:36:47,543 --> 00:36:49,413
La verdad...

739
00:36:50,128 --> 00:36:52,210
La verdad...

740
00:36:53,068 --> 00:36:58,238
Llama tanto la atención...

741
00:36:58,298 --> 00:37:01,108
que un gobierno
haya querido negociar

742
00:37:01,168 --> 00:37:03,124
con dictadores genocidas,

743
00:37:03,184 --> 00:37:06,016
